  _showInfo: 1
  _explanation: "Reset Level\n----------------\nWhen a collision with a trigger with
    tags [Enemy] starts:\n          Sets the current velocity of Player to a speed
    of 0 units/sec, in the current direction.\n          disables component Player
    (OkapiKit.MovementPlatformer)\n          sets animation parameter IsDead of object
    Player to True\n          plays sound dead at volume 1 and at pitch 1\n then,
    at 1,5 seconds, \n          switches to scene Level 1\n"
